code: export const MinutesPassed=date=>{const date1=new Date();const date2=new Date(date);const diffTime=date2-date1;return diffTime/(1000*60);};export const GetDateString=date=>{let d=null;d=date?new Date(date):new Date();let month=''+(d.getMonth()+1),day=''+d.getDate(),year=d.getFullYear(),hours=d.getHours(),mins=d.getMinutes();if(month>=1&month<=9)month='0'+month.toString();if(day>=0&day<=9)day='0'+day.toString();if(hours>=0&hours<=9)hours='0'+hours.toString();if(mins>=0&mins<=9)mins='0'+mins.toString();return[year,month,day].join('-')+'T'+[hours,mins].join(':');};
